synopsis: Nanami revels in her memory of her kiss with Tomoe, but then quickly reminds herself that he swore he'd never fall in love with a human. Nanami then over-hears a conversation involving Tomoe. Chaos ensues.
Nanami wants to take a holiday, Tomoe agrees on a day trip. Nanami overhears a conversation between her familiars. Thusly, wanting to prove herself useful the antics unfold.
